Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.72,0:01:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我是魯索，請留言{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}This is Russo. Please leave a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.86,0:01:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他不回我電話{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}He's not answering my calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.56,0:01:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}玩完了，他一定知道{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}It's over, and he must know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.89,0:01:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你不認為他能夠重新振作？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You don't think  there's any way he can recover?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.16,0:01:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}從現在起到11月5日  共和黨會在每個電台和電視台{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}The Republicans will play that interview  on every radio and television station
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.37,0:01:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}播放專訪{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}from now until November 5th.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.50,0:01:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我很同情那年輕人  不過我一開始就有疑慮{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I sympathize with the kid,  but this was my concern from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.47,0:01:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}長官，我應該聽你的話{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}And I should've listened to you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.91,0:01:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我以為他可以耐住壓力{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I thought he could handle the pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.55,0:02:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}所以他退出，我們得找人替代{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Okay. So he withdraws.  We need to replace him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.18,0:02:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}有任何建議嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You have any ideas?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.52,0:02:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}只剩不到兩個月的時間？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}With less than two months to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.39,0:02:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}如果總統沒有  在早先的討論把我剔除{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}If the President hadn't  shut me out of the early discussions,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我早就想出一些不錯的人選{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I could've come up with some good options,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.79,0:02:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我真不知道誰既有知名度  又有獻金基礎{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}but I don't know anyone who's got  the name recognition and donor base
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.53,0:02:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}能在七周時間內  開始準備競選{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}to start a campaign  from scratch just seven weeks out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.13,0:02:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}讓我來想想{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Let me think.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.84,0:02:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}船到橋頭自然直{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Everything hinges on the next few minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.91,0:02:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我好幾個月的計劃  採取的行動，都是這樣來的{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}All my months of planning,  every move I've made.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.35,0:02:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 有個人選  - 誰？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-There is one person.  -Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.02,0:02:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}就是你，副總統{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You, Mr. Vice President.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.46,0:02:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}如果你再次競選  應該可以大勝{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}If you ran to reclaim your seat,  I think you'd win by a landslide.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.43,0:02:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}要辭去副總統一職？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Resign the Vice Presidency?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.06,0:02:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}只有你贏才能如此{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Only ifyou win.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.46,0:02:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}沃克需要我搭檔競選2016年{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Walker needs me for 2016.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.03,0:02:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你確定他會邀你搭檔？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Are you entirely certain  he's gonna keep you on the ticket?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.90,0:02:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你們兩個不太合{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I mean, it's no secret
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.57,0:03:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}這不是什麼秘密{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}the two of you don't exactly get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.11,0:03:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他說了什麼？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}What has he said?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.28,0:03:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}副總統，你讓我很為難{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Oh, you're putting me in a very  awkward position, Mr. Vice President.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.48,0:03:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他說我壞話？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Has he been bad-mouthing me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.12,0:03:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他說「很難搞」{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Well, the exact phrase  he used was "pain in the ass."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.26,0:03:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}渾蛋{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}That fucker.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.63,0:03:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他根本不知領導為何物  不懂得尊重{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}He's got no idea how to lead,  no sense of respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.74,0:03:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 是他的意思？  - 不{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-ls this his idea?  -No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.20,0:03:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 他要擺脫我？  - 我昨天才想到{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-His way of getting rid of me?  -No. It struck me yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.51,0:03:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}覺得可以提出來建議{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}and I just thought it was worth suggesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.24,0:03:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}不過我還沒和任何人討論過{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}But, no, I haven't  discussed this with anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.04,0:03:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你是不該討論  民眾也不允許副總統變成州長{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}And you shouldn't. People don't leave  the White House to become a governor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.02,0:03:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}長官，能否請教一個私人問題？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}May I ask you a personal question, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.79,0:03:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你想當副總統嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Do you want to be the Vice President?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.02,0:03:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}彼得說你投入那場競選時{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Peter said that when you were  out on that campaign trail,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.86,0:03:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你非常熱心又活力十足{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}you had so much enthusiasm and energy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.46,0:03:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他覺得你可能  很想念當州長的日子{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}that he thought you maybe  missed being the Governor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.54,0:04:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我是很想念{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I do miss it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.77,0:04:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你何不回去？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Then why not go back?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.61,0:04:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你會在這場選舉裏成為英雄{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You could be the hero of this election
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.01,0:04:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}同時在2016年為民主黨  在賓州保住一席{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}and secure Pennsylvania  for the Democrats in 2016.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.05,0:04:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}就算葛瑞很討厭我{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Garrett would never go  along with something like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.32,0:04:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他絕不會做這樣的事{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}even if he hates my guts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.92,0:04:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}這會讓他顯得很弱  像是他無法掌控管理團隊{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}It would make him look weak,  like he's lost control of the administration.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.32,0:04:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}如果是雙方的決定  就不會如此{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Not if it was a mutual decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.89,0:04:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我來跟葛瑞談  我不會跟他說我們談過{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Look, let me talk to Garrett.  I won't mention that we've spoken.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.67,0:04:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}瞭解他的想法  應該不會有什麼問題{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I suppose there's no harm in  finding out what he thinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.14,0:04:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}副總統，謝謝{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Thank you, Mr. Vice President.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.28,0:04:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 賞金四百元的標語  - 1976年「他讓我們再度驕傲」{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Slogans for $400.  -1976. "He's making us proud again. "
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.52,0:04:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 艾傑  - 誰是卡特？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-A.J.  -Who is Carter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.35,0:04:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 約翰是誰？  - 誰是福特？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-No. John?  -Who's Ford?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.69,0:04:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}彼得？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Peter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.35,0:04:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}賞金六百元的標語{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Slogans for $600.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.86,0:04:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}彼得，你在嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Peter, are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.16,0:04:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}「班足以勝任總統」{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}"Grandfather's hat fits Ben. "
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.89,0:05:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 克勞蒂亞  - 班傑明哈里森是誰？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Claudia.  -Who is Benjamin Harrison?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.93,0:05:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 對  - 賞金八百元的總統競選標語{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Yes.  -Presidential Slogans for $800.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.90,0:05:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}1900年「完美服務」{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}1900. "The full dinner pail. "
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.50,0:05:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我搭火車時，差點報警  要他們破門而入{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}On the train ride down, I almost  called the police to have them break in
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.27,0:05:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}確定你沒有自殘{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}and make sure you hadn't hurt yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.41,0:05:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我不會問你發生什麼事  現在這不重要{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I'm not even gonna ask you what happened.  It doesn't matter right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.31,0:05:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}現在重要的是…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}What matters right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.48,0:05:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 重要的是…  - 誰是戈德華特？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-What matters...  -Who is Goldwater?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.32,0:05:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 克勞蒂亞  - 誰是戈德華特？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Claudia.  -Who is Goldwater?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.79,0:05:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}巴利戈德華特{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Barry Goldwater. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.45,0:05:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 銳利如刀，賞金八百元  - 正式方式…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Cuts Like a Knife for $800.  -The official instrument...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.66,0:05:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}別這樣，我正在看{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Oh, come on. Hey, I'm watching that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.00,0:05:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}重要的是你屋前的50名記者{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}What matters is the 50 reporters  in front of your building
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.17,0:05:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}還有150名不知道自己是否  還有工作的競選工作人員{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}and the 150 campaign staffers  who don't know if they still have a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.87,0:05:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}玩完了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.01,0:05:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我知道{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.18,0:05:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}叫他們離開{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}So, tell them to go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.79,0:06:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你打算躲在這裏  希望事情自行落幕？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}What, are you just gonna hole yourself  up in here and hope it all goes away?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.56,0:06:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我就是這麼打算{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Yeah, that's pretty much the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.20,0:06:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我不允許{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Well, I won't let you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.80,0:06:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}放下{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Hey, put that down. Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.37,0:06:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 放下！  - 彼得…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Hey, put that down!  -Peter...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.29,0:06:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們得發表聲明{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We need to put out a statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.59,0:06:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你準備好時打電話給我{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Call me when you're prepared to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.73,0:06:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我會在費城的總部{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I'll be at the headquarters in Philly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.17,0:06:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我怕愛上你{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I was scared that I was starting to feel  too much for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.24,0:06:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}所以才會結束{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I think, that's why I ended it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.18,0:06:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你不允許害怕嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}And you have no room for fear?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.18,0:07:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}一害怕就成事不足{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}No. Being afraid  doesn't accomplish anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.05,0:07:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}不對，我在國外時  合理的害怕疾病或暴力{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}It's not true. When I'm overseas,  rational fear of disease or violence,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.12,0:07:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}這種害怕讓你得以生存{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}that sort of fear keeps you alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.69,0:07:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}回到這裏，我發現自己{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Back here, God, I find myself afraid of things
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.66,0:07:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}不知在怕什麼{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}that I can't name or point to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.27,0:07:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}那就是，我有多渺小？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}It's like, how little am I seeing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.97,0:07:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}或我浪費了今天或當下？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Or have I wasted this day or this moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.74,0:07:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我有時會想  我的生命是否有價值{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Yeah, I think that sometimes,  whether my life will add up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.45,0:07:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}法蘭斯要是聽到這樣的話  會覺得很蠢{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Francis would roll his eyes  if he heard me talking like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.82,0:07:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他知道你在哪裏嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Does he know where you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.32,0:07:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他不知道{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}No, he doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.54,0:07:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}要是他找你，你應該在那裏{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}If he's looking for you, that's where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.34,0:07:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}在那邊{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.91,0:08:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}在你遇到法蘭之前{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Before you met Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.38,0:08:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}一個人{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.98,0:08:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}生性好奇{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.95,0:08:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}求知若渴{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Absorbing everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.42,0:08:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你絕對想不到我年輕時的樣子{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You have no idea  what I was like when I was a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.92,0:08:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他知道你的那一面嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Did he ever know that side ofyou?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.39,0:08:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他對於我的那一面沒興趣{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}He wasn't interested in that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.60,0:08:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我也沒有{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}And neither was l.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.83,0:08:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你對什麼有興趣？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}What were you interested in?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.47,0:08:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}不只是個觀察者{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Being more than an observer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.27,0:08:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你希望被看見{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You wanted to be seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.57,0:08:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}不只被看見{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Not just seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.41,0:08:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我想成為重要人物{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I wanted to be significant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.72,0:08:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}沒有慣例可循{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}There's no historical precedent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.69,0:08:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}艾朗布爾競選州長  卡霍競選參議員{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Aaron Burr ran for governor,  Calhoun for the Senate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.12,0:08:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}兩百年前，一個在槍戰殺死人  另一個支持蓄奴{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Two hundred years ago. One shot a man  in a duel, the other believed in slavery.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.93,0:08:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}法蘭，我們要跟他們一樣嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Is that really the sort of  company we want to share, Frank?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.16,0:08:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}總統，我們可能會輸掉  相當有影響力的一州{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Mr. President, we stand losing  control of an important swing state,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.53,0:08:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}眾議院多數和你的競選連任{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}our majority in the House, and quite  possibly your second term in office.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.33,0:09:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}想要選贏得使出非常手段{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Preventing all of that may  require unconventional measures.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.27,0:09:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}這像是要除掉他{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}It would look like I'm pushing him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.07,0:09:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}或更糟的辭職{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Or worse,  that he's abandoning the administration.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.64,0:09:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你們一起發表聲明{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You make a joint statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.38,0:09:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你宣佈除非他選贏  否則不會辭職{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You say he won't resign unless he wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.18,0:09:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}要是選輸了，他仍是副總統{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}If he loses, he stays on as Vice President.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.92,0:09:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}沒有人會責怪你們  對彼此不忠誠{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}No one could accuse either of you  of disloyalty to the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.42,0:09:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 吉姆跟你提這個想法？  - 完全是我想的{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Did Jim come to you with this?  -No. It's entirely my idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.19,0:09:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}在跟副總統講之前  我一定要先跟你提才行{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I wouldn't dream of speaking to the Vice  President without passing it by you first.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.39,0:09:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我想他會認為這是種侮辱{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I think he'd take it as an affront,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.56,0:09:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}像是我要趕走他{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Iike I'm trying to get rid of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.93,0:09:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}老實說，我想他會有興趣  超乎你想像{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Honestly, sir, I think he might be  more interested than you imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.17,0:09:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 為什麼？  - 我不太想提{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Why is that?  -Well, I hesitate to bring this up,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.77,0:09:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}不過當他為魯索競選時{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}but when he was campaigning for Russo,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.34,0:09:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他說了你不少事{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}he spoke quite freely about you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.92,0:09:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}告訴我{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.05,0:09:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}當然我是從彼得那裏聽來的{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Of course, I'm getting  this secondhand from Peter,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.99,0:09:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}不過重點在…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}but the gist of it is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.16,0:09:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你完全缺乏領導能力{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}That you lack entirely in leadership,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.86,0:09:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}也不懂得尊重{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}and that you have no sense of respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.96,0:10:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他想要更多職責？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}And he wants more responsibility?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.23,0:10:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他欠缺思慮、不守規矩  我如何賦予他重任？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}And how do I give him that when he shows  absolutely no discretion, no discipline?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.23,0:10:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}這就是我的重點  我完全負起支持魯索的責任{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Well, that is entirely my point. Now, look,  I take full responsibility for backing Russo,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.54,0:10:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}不過事情總會有轉機{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}but there could be a silver lining in all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.21,0:10:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你可以完成兩個目標{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You could accomplish two goals.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.08,0:10:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}為民主黨保住賓州{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Secure Pennsylvania for the Democrats
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.68,0:10:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}同時找出顧及情面的方法  換掉馬修{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}and find an honorable  way to replace Matthews.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.45,0:10:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你認為呢？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.09,0:10:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}這是很重大的決定  我們不想急就章{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I think it is a very big decision,  and we do not want to make it impulsively.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.86,0:10:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}同意，我想多做些考量{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I agree.  I'd like to put some more thought into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.36,0:10:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}長官，這麼做很審慎  請記住{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Well, that is very prudent, sir.  Just bear in mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.39,0:10:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}只有七周，每一天都很重要{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}seven weeks out, that every day counts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.24,0:10:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 先生  - 這個多少錢？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Hi, sir.  -How much is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.44,0:10:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我這裏有你的收據{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Oh, I got your receipt right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.35,0:11:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}不，只有40元{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}No, no, no. It was just $40.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.86,0:11:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}不要告訴別人，好嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Yeah. Don't tell anyone, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.49,0:11:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我絕不會透露房客的事{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}No. I never say anything about our tenants.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.96,0:11:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 媒體仍在外頭？  - 對{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-The press still outside?  -Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.67,0:11:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}按照你的意思  我告訴他們你不在{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I told them you weren't here, like you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.70,0:11:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他們大部分都離開  不過還有幾個沒走{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Most of them left. There's still a few, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.64,0:11:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}如果我要離開  有地方能不被看見嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}If I wanted to leave, is there a place  I could do it without being seen?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.51,0:11:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}有，到車庫的防火電梯{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Yeah. The freight elevator  down to the garage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.24,0:11:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 我可以幫你叫計程車…  - 謝謝，有需要我會讓你知道{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-I could call you a cab or...  -All right. Thanks. I'll let you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.61,0:11:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}魯索先生…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Mr. Russo...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.78,0:11:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}先生，這不關我的事{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Sir, it's none of my business,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.09,0:11:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}不過我叔叔戒酒失敗過幾次{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}but my uncle,  he fell off the wagon a few times.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.32,0:11:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}這時，他最想身邊有人陪{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}When he did, the best thing  for him was just not to be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.09,0:11:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我不會收你的錢  我會分擔你的重擔{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I'll give you this money back,  I'll take that bag offyour hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.69,0:11:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}進來這裏，與你作伴…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}come in here, keep you company...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.16,0:11:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}非常感謝，如果我改變心意  會告知你{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I appreciate it.  I'll let you know if I change my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.28,0:13:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}坐下{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.18,0:13:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}克萊兒在哪？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Where's Claire?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.22,0:13:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}不在這裏{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.12,0:13:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}這是什麼？收尾嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}So what is this, tying up loose ends?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.89,0:13:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我不亂做臆測  像你這樣的人，不容易瞭解{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I wouldn't presume.  People like you can't be neatly tied up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.96,0:13:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}不過我想我們可能可以…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}But I thought perhaps we could start...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.19,0:14:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}很有品味{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}It's very tasteful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.53,0:15:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}她穿這件去慈善會{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}This is the dress she wore to the gala.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.54,0:15:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我相信{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I believe so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.37,0:15:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}的確如此{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.77,0:15:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我認得{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I recognize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.25,0:15:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}回去臥室{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Go back into the bedroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.87,0:15:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我很訝異  你把她拍得如此清楚{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I'm amazed how well you got her in focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.58,0:15:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}該稱她什麼？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}What should we call her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.68,0:15:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}為何要名字？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Why does she need a name?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.89,0:16:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我從不為無名氏拍照{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I never photograph anyone  without knowing their name.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.92,0:16:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你不拍這種照片，但是我拍{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You didn't take the photograph. I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.46,0:16:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們該稱她為克萊兒{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I think we should call her Claire.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.20,0:16:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}她根本和我不像{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}She doesn't even look like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.14,0:16:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}也不像年輕的我  你為什麼一直這樣說？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Not even a younger version.  Why do you keep saying that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.40,0:16:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}無關她的面貌、表情{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Not her features, her expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.41,0:16:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們應該把相片裱起來  你可以把她掛在你家{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Hey, we should mount it.  You can hang her in your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.34,0:16:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}法蘭斯會反對嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Would Francis object?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.12,0:16:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}可以不要討論法蘭斯嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Can we please not discuss Francis?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.62,0:16:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}是你在公園提起他{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You brought him up in the park.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.99,0:16:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我知道，我不該如此{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I know I did, and I shouldn't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.16,0:16:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}所以我們得假裝他不存在？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}So we have to pretend he doesn't exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.50,0:16:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我以為我們什麼都可以談{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I thought we could talk about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.47,0:16:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他是存在的，你必須承認{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}He is a presence here. You must admit that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.07,0:16:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}當你昨天走進門時{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}When you walked  through the door yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.31,0:16:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他馬上跟著你走進來{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}he walked right in with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.78,0:17:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}只有我，沒有別人{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}It's just me, nobody else.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.32,0:17:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你一直這樣告訴自己  可能會成真{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You keep telling yourself that,  it might come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.82,0:17:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}如果她知道我穿這件  會怎麼想？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}How do you think she'd feel  if she knew I was wearing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.13,0:17:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}不知道{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.03,0:17:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你覺得她會不高興嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You don't think she'd be upset?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.24,0:17:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}她可能會說你穿很漂亮{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}She'd probably say  you look very beautiful in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.34,0:17:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}硬梆梆的{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}It's like steel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.71,0:17:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你應該放回去{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You should put it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.02,0:17:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我要留著{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I think I'll keep it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.12,0:17:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你要的話，我會買一件給你{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I'll buy you one ofyour own, ifyou'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.09,0:17:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}不，我要這件{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}No. I want this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.76,0:17:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}她去過我的臥房  應該知道我來過她的臥房{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}She came into my bedroom.  She should know I came into hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.27,0:17:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你的床鋪向來都這麼整齊嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Is your bed always so perfectly made?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.07,0:18:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}這是我念軍校時養成的習慣{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}It's a habit I formed at military school.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.31,0:18:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}她睡哪一邊？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}What side of the bed does she sleep on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.28,0:18:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}那邊{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}That side.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.03,0:18:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}她可以留著{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}She can keep it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.04,0:18:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}更適合她{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Fits her better anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.72,0:19:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}聽好，喬伊…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Listen, Zoe...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.09,0:19:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}不管樓上發生什麼事  或是過去六個月的情形{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Whatever just happened upstairs,  whatever these past six months have been,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.52,0:19:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們能把事情單純化嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}can we agree that it is time to simplify?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.80,0:19:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}單純化會是什麼樣子？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}What does simple look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.40,0:19:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們保持專業的安排{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We maintain our professional arrangement,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.10,0:19:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}如你建議，我會照辦{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}as you suggested, which I will honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.14,0:19:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你仍信任我？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You still trust me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.01,0:19:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我還有其他選擇嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}What choice do I have?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.95,0:19:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你沒有像你說的傷害我  或棄我不顧{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You didn't hurt me  or discard me like you said you would.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.76,0:19:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}很高興我不必如此{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I'm glad I didn't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.13,0:20:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們都同意要單純化{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Yes, we'll agree to simplify.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.93,0:20:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}好{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.72,0:20:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}法蘭，抱歉我來晚幾分鐘{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Sorry I'm a few minutes late, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.13,0:20:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}請坐{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Please, have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.50,0:20:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我很清楚  你要求這次見面的原因{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I have a pretty good idea why  you asked for this meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.34,0:20:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你和總統談過了嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Have you and the President  had a chance to speak?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.01,0:20:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}談過了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We have.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.61,0:20:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 他有偏向哪一方嗎？  - 他難以抉擇{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-ls he leaning one way or another?  -He's torn.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.61,0:20:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 你呢？  - 比他好一點{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-And what about you?  -I'm a little less torn.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.61,0:20:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我的直覺告訴我，這樣不對{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}My instincts tell me it's a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.98,0:20:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你想說服我換個方式？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You want to convince me otherwise?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.49,0:21:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}如果你的直覺認為  這樣行不通，我不打算…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Well, look, if your instincts tell you  this is not the way to go, I'm not about to...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.26,0:21:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}法蘭，我要問你  兩個很直接的問題{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Frank, I'm gonna ask you  two very direct questions,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.26,0:21:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}也希望得到坦白的回答{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}and I would appreciate direct answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.99,0:21:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}當你讓我兒子進大學{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}When you got my son into college,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.10,0:21:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}有預期這樣的時刻嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}were you anticipating a moment like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.43,0:21:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}不懂{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I don't follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.47,0:21:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}法蘭，請老實說？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Honestly, Frank?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.24,0:21:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我有預期…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Was I antici...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.01,0:21:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}如果能瞭解你在問什麼  我很樂於據實以告{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I would be happy to answer you  directly if I knew what you were asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.58,0:21:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我問你第二個問題{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}All right. I will ask you my second question.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.65,0:21:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你想當副總統嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Do you want the  Vice Presidency for yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.15,0:21:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}這得看總統的意願，他是否…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I would serve at the pleasure  of the President. If that was his...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.36,0:21:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你提出這個建議  好讓自己取代馬修{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You proposed this idea so that  you can take Matthews' place.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.96,0:21:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 我沒那樣說  - 但是你想要的{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-I did not say that.  -But it is what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.53,0:21:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 我要的是…  - 總統讓你當副手{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-What I want is in the...  -The President makes you VP,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.13,0:21:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他讓你一起在2016年競選{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}he keeps you on the ticket in 2016,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.07,0:21:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你以此當作  2020年的競選跳板{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}and you use that as a  springboard to run in 2020.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.64,0:21:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}告訴我  你心中不曾想過這種途徑{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Tell me that trajectory  has never entered your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.27,0:21:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}琳達，我習慣{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Well, Linda, I make a habit of
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.08,0:21:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}從任何假設情境  設想所有途徑{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}considering all trajectories  in any given situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.58,0:22:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}但那是務實的做法  不是私人的做法{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}But that's a practical exercise,  not a personal one.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.05,0:22:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}所以你拒絕承認{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}So you refuse to admit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.32,0:22:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}承認那是我要的？  這根本不相干{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Admit it's what I want? That's irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.32,0:22:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}是你要求開這場會議，不是我{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You're the one who asked  for this meeting, not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.42,0:22:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}這場會議是想要解決問題{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}This meeting's about  trying to solve a problem,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.36,0:22:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}而不是滿足某種個人野心{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}not fulfill some personal ambition.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.53,0:22:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}要是兩者都能達成  你也不會拒絕{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}But if both could be achieved,  you wouldn't object.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.83,0:22:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}不管總統要誰去取代馬修{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I think this is a sound course of action
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.83,0:22:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我想這是很安全的行動路線{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}regardless ofwho the President  taps to replace Matthews.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.67,0:22:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我必須賭下目前擁有的一切{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I must gamble everything I have right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.07,0:22:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我若老實說  她會拿來對付我{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}If I'm honest, she may use it against me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.68,0:22:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}如我不老實說  她不會採取行動{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}If I'm not, she won't lift a finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.88,0:22:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我自己也用這樣的策略{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I've used this same tactic myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.71,0:22:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}人一旦被攤在陽光下  就會任人宰割{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Once someone is exposed,  they're at your mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.05,0:22:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}她要我這樣說{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}She wants to hear me say the words.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.23,0:22:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}對{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.06,0:22:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我想當副總統{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I want to be the Vice President.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.10,0:22:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我幫助你兒子進大學  希望你能有所回饋{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}And, yes, I helped your son get into college  in the hopes that you would return the favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.81,0:23:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}然而我不能逼你這麼做{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}But I can't force you to do so, Linda.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.88,0:23:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}但我認為我們  能組成令人畏懼的團隊{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}But I also think that  we would make a formidable team.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.75,0:23:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}看看我們的成績{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Look what we've been able to accomplish
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.09,0:23:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}就算處境艱困也有一番作為{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}even when we've been  at odds with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.96,0:23:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}想想如果我們不合作  能完成什麼{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Now put your mind to what  we could accomplish if we weren't.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.97,0:23:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}琳達，謝謝你的時間{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Thank you for taking the time, Linda.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.41,0:23:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我再打給你，事情如何？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I'll call you back. How'd it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.71,0:23:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}她不動聲色{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}She's holding her cards  very close to the chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.15,0:23:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 有彼得的消息嗎？  - 沒有{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Any word from Peter?  -Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.58,0:23:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}克裏絲汀娜說他躲在公寓{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Christina said he wouldn't  leave the apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.02,0:23:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我打給警衛室  他說彼得已經離開了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}But I called the doorman,  and he said that Peter was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.25,0:23:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 去哪裏？  - 他不知道{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Where?  -He doesn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.85,0:23:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他必須正式退出  才能對沃克施壓{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}He needs to officially withdraw  to put pressure on Walker.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.56,0:23:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我正試著找到他{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I'm trying to track him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.92,0:23:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你怎麼一開始讓他跑了？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Why'd you let him  out of your sight in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.59,0:23:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我以為他在沖澡  他趁我和你講電話時溜掉{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I thought he was showering. He disappeared  when I was on the phone with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.33,0:23:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}道格，計劃原本是  他競選失利，然後退出{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}There was a plan here, Doug.  He explodes, he withdraws,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.67,0:24:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們讓他再試一次  他悄悄引退{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}we put him back together,  and he quietly goes away.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.10,0:24:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}自從媒體指控魯索  昨天早上接受匹茲堡{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Russo has made no public appearances  since allegations that he was inebriated
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.27,0:24:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}WZPZ電台專訪時酒醉  他就神隱起來{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}during a radio interview  on WZPZ Pittsburgh yesterday morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.58,0:24:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}民主黨領導群有些人建議{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Sources among  the Democratic leadership have suggested
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.28,0:24:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}政黨目前考慮找人取代魯索{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}that the party is currently  considering options to replace Russo.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.75,0:24:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}同時共和黨候選人  傑克史沃佛特的領先支持度{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Meanwhile, Republican candidate  Jack Swofford's lead
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.75,0:24:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}根據CNN當夜選民民意調查{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}has jumped to a 24-point margin,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.96,0:24:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}已經躍升到24個百分點{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}according to an overnight  CNN poll of registered voters.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.72,0:24:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}史沃佛特的競選團隊  也提供一則勁爆消息{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}The Swofford campaign is also reporting  a sharp spike in contributions.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.93,0:24:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}將近50萬元在過去20…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Nearly $500, 000 in the last 20...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.73,0:24:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}魯索尚未出面，競選未定{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.90,0:24:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我今早看到這個{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I saw that this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.67,0:24:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}法蘭斯力推彼得競選{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Francis got Peter to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.11,0:24:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你和他很熟嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Do you know him well?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.48,0:24:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}不熟{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We weren't close.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.22,0:24:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你需要打電話嗎？  我可以到其他房間{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Do you need to make calls?  'Cause I can head into the other room.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.36,0:25:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}不必了，謝謝{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I don't think so. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.28,0:25:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}去哪裏？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.55,0:25:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}到攝影棚，我今天應該去那裏{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}To the lab. I should've gone in today.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.95,0:25:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}亞當{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Adam.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.09,0:25:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 亞當…  - 去吧，快去{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Adam...  -Just go. Go. Leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.09,0:25:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你覺得這可以維持多久？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}How long do you think this  can possibly go on for?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.33,0:25:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們不曾相處超過48小時{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We have never spent more  than 48 hours together.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.43,0:25:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}也許有理由這樣做{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Maybe there's a reason for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.43,0:25:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我有部分仍愛著你{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}A part of me still loves you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.40,0:25:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}哪部分？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Which part?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.68,0:25:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}克萊兒，我不能當急救站{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I can't be just a pit stop, Claire,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.05,0:25:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 或像是逃避…  - 別說了，你不只這樣{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-or some sort of escape...  -Oh, come on. You're more than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.38,0:25:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}或是彌補法蘭斯不足之處{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Or a top-up on  whatever Francis can't provide.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.35,0:25:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}閉嘴！亞當，他是我老公{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Oh, fuck off! He's my husband, Adam.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.79,0:26:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們經歷的事  遠比你能想像的還多{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We've gone through more  than you could ever imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.32,0:26:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我忌妒你的自由精神  深受吸引，不是人人都能這樣{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I envy your free spirit, and I'm attracted to it,  but not all of us have that luxury.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.16,0:26:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}克萊兒，所以我對你  才會這麼絕望{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Which is what I find  so frustrating about you, Claire.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.76,0:26:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你做了選擇{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You had a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.47,0:26:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}選擇不自由{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You chose not to be free.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.37,0:26:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我選擇的是能讓我  愛超過一周的男人{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}No. What I chose was a man  I could love for more than a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.64,0:26:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我不該那麼說，我…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I shouldn't have said that. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.21,0:26:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}至少你很誠實{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}At least you're being honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.11,0:26:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}亞當，我無法像你一樣  只活在當下{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I can't live moment to  moment like you, Adam.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.05,0:26:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我過去和法蘭斯在一起  也會和他共創未來{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I have a history with Francis,  I have a future with him,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.02,0:26:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}這比當下更長遠{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}and it's bigger than a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.36,0:26:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}那麼你該扼殺愛意{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Then you should kill it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.56,0:26:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}不管你的哪一部分仍愛我{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Whatever part of you still loves me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.37,0:26:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}如果你做不到{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}If you can't,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.20,0:26:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}就由我來{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.38,0:26:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 亞當…  - 別說了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Adam...  -No.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.87,0:27:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 哪位？  - 甜心{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Hello?  -Hey. Hey, sweetie.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.28,0:27:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你好嗎？媽媽也在嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}How's it going? Are you with your mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.51,0:27:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}她在樓下，要找她嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}She's downstairs.  You want me to go get her?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.75,0:27:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}不用，我只是打來{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}No. No. I just wanted to call and say,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.02,0:27:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}問你和弟弟好不好{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}you know, hey to your brother and you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.36,0:27:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他在嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Is he there?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.73,0:27:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我想他在他的房間裏{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}He's in his room, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.50,0:27:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}去叫他聽電話{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Okay. You want to go get him?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.47,0:27:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}等一下{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.08,0:28:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他說不想和你說話{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}He says he doesn't want to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.72,0:28:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 為什麼？  - 爸，我們看了新聞{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Why not?  -We've seen the news, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.05,0:28:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}昨天學校來了一大堆電視記者{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}There were all sorts of  TV cameras at our school yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.09,0:28:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}媽要我們這周待在家裏{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Mom's making us stay home this week.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.53,0:28:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我要你做件事，我要你{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I want you to do something.  I want you to go to
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.84,0:28:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}到臥室的窗戶往外看{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}your bedroom window and look out.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.88,0:28:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}有看到黑色的車嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You see that black car?
