Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.91,0:31:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}先生，如果警察讓你走  我們現在不能逮捕你{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Well, if you were let go, sir,  we can't arrest you for it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.15,0:31:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我酒駕來這裏  以這個罪名逮捕我{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Well, I drunk drove here. Arrest me for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.92,0:31:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們能送你到戒酒…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We can put you in a detox tank...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.32,0:31:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我要正式逮捕{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I want to be formally arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.09,0:31:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我是議員彼得魯索{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}My name is Congressman Peter Russo.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.90,0:31:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我一月在密西根大道被捕{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I was arrested in January  on Michigan Avenue.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.11,0:31:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}議員，請坐{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Please have a seat, Congressman.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.44,0:32:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我得打幾通電話{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I gotta make a few phone calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.68,0:33:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 你找到他了嗎？  - 我在他前妻的家門前{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Have you found him?  -I'm in front of his ex-wife's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.28,0:33:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}克裏絲汀娜說  他從那裏打電話{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}But Christina said he called from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.91,0:33:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 他不在哪裏？  - 不在{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-He's not there?  -No.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.88,0:33:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}不過我在路邊發現他的電話{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}But his phone is. I found it by the curb.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.72,0:33:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們沒辦法和他連絡？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}So we have no way to contact him?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.22,0:33:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}除非他要找我們{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Not unless he reaches out to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.72,0:33:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 這可不妙  - 要我報警嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-This isn't good.  -Want me to alert the authorities?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.86,0:33:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}再給他一點時間{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Let's give him a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.63,0:33:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 要多久？  - 大概六個月{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-How long did it last?  -About six months.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.23,0:33:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 他比較年長  - 大很多歲？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-He was older.  -A lot?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.64,0:33:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}對{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.24,0:33:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他是記者，還是在白宮工作？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Was he a journalist,  or did he work on the Hill?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.58,0:33:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我不方便說{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I'd rather not say.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.28,0:33:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}好吧{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.45,0:33:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我曾經很愛慕他{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}He was someone I looked up to for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.59,0:33:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}為什麼分手？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Why did it end?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.59,0:33:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他有老婆{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}He has a wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.20,0:33:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們知道遲早要結束{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We both knew it was going to end eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.27,0:34:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}這真的…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I mean, it was really...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.77,0:34:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}一團糟{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}It was fucked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.94,0:34:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們第一次一起過夜時{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}The first night we spent together,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.41,0:34:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他說他會傷害我，然後拋棄我{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}he told me he was gonna  hurt me and then discard me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.71,0:34:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}當關係結束時  我說這兩件事都沒發生{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}And when it ended,  I told him that he'd done neither.
