Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.89,0:34:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你不能對我許這種諾言{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Yeah, you can't promise me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.86,0:34:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我可以{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Yes, I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.46,0:34:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 有誰看到他嗎？  - 沒有{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Has anyone else seen him?  -No.
