Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.24,0:34:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我真不該蹚渾水{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I never should've got mixed up  in this fucking mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.11,0:34:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}邦尼，我們沒時間後悔{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We're way behind regret time, Barney.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.81,0:34:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}吩咐你的手下掩護他{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Just have your guys keep him out of sight.
