Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.48,0:35:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 找到他了，謝謝  - 好{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-I got him. Thanks.  -Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.34,0:35:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}來{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Come on.
