Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.30,0:35:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 從這裏？  - 對{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-This way?  -Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.44,0:35:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}彼得，你到底在想什麼？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}What were you thinking, Peter?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.11,0:35:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我需要為我的行動負責{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I need to take responsibility for my actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.32,0:36:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}讓自己入獄？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}By getting yourself thrown in jail?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.12,0:36:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}真正的責任{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Real responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.56,0:36:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}像他們在會議中說的實話{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Like they talk about in the meetings,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.36,0:36:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}而不是我們為競選說的謊言{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}not the lies we told for the campaign.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.16,0:36:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你剛剛的行為完全不顧後果{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}What you just did was extremely reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.26,0:36:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我不在乎{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I don't care.
