Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.11,0:36:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}這樣還不夠…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}That's not enough. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.61,0:36:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我不要再躲藏{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I need to stop hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.69,0:36:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們來一起想台詞{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Well, let's work together on the language.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.76,0:36:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我得自己想，說出自己的話{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I have to do it on my own.  It's gotta be in my own words.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.59,0:36:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}彼得，這不再是  你一個人的事了吧？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Look, Peter, this isn't just  about you anymore, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.33,0:36:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 讓我幫你  - 我不要你幫{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Let me help you.  -I don't want your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.10,0:36:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}當我被逮捕時  也不曾要求你幫我{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I didn't ever ask your help  when I got arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.97,0:36:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你的幫忙什麼時候幫過我？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}When has your help ever helped me?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.81,0:36:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你可以照你想要的方式過生活{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You can live your life the way you want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.14,0:36:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我不想再受人擺佈{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I'm done being told how to live mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.62,0:37:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}一定有可以不需要毀了一切{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Well, there has to be  a way to take responsibility
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.98,0:37:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}才能負責任的方法{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}without shattering everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.69,0:37:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你願意至少討論一下嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Are you at least willing  to have that discussion?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.49,0:37:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 要我上樓嗎？  - 不要{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Do you want me to come upstairs?  -No.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.21,0:38:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}彼得，我知道你很痛苦{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I know you're in a lot of pain, Peter.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.02,0:38:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}但是我不希望你今晚感到痛苦{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}But I don't want you to feel any pain tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.82,0:38:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你可以有個嶄新的明天{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Here. You can start fresh tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.52,0:38:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}說吧，我不會批判你  我甚至和你同一陣線{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Go ahead. I won't judge you.  Hell, I'll even join you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.93,0:38:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}放鬆{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Just relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.37,0:38:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}現在到家了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You're home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.24,0:38:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}不管你明天要面對什麼{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Whatever it is you have to face tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.31,0:38:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}現在都不必面對{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}you don't have to face it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.42,0:38:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}現在只有你和我{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Right now, it's just you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.26,0:38:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}其餘的都不重要{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}The rest of the world doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.33,0:38:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你的孩子、克裏絲汀娜{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Your children, Christina,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.20,0:39:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他們會原諒你{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}they will forgive you,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.50,0:39:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}因為他們愛你，彼得{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}because you're loved, Peter.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.64,0:39:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}毀了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.48,0:39:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我毀了自己{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I failed myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.85,0:39:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}毀了我的家庭{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I failed my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.45,0:39:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}毀了競選{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I failed the campaign.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.45,0:39:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}彼得，沒那麼糟{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}No, you haven't, Peter.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.26,0:39:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我可以喝嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}May l?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.41,0:39:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我和克萊兒結婚時{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You know,  when Claire and I were first married,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.35,0:39:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們就談到生小孩的事{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}we talked about having children.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.82,0:39:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我很坦白地說  我不要任何小孩{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I told her flat out I didn't want any.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.52,0:39:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}雖然很自私卻很誠實{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}It was selfish but honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.56,0:39:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我的童年不快樂{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I didn't have a particularly happy childhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.26,0:40:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我想你的童年也不快樂{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I suspect you didn't either.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.49,0:40:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}是不快樂{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.86,0:40:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}看吧，人都會有痛苦{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You see, no person avoids pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.43,0:40:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}既然知道童年不快樂  就不需要讓孩子受苦{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}And I just didn't think it was right  to bring a child in knowing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.00,0:40:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}現在回想起來，我…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}But now when I think back, l...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.71,0:40:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}明白那是懦弱{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I realize that was cowardly.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.51,0:40:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我看到你{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I see you,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.92,0:40:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}想著，這是個勇敢的男人  比我勇敢多了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}and I think, well, there's a brave man,  far braver than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.25,0:40:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我好害怕{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I'm so tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.63,0:40:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}當我想到…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}When I think about...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.00,0:40:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我好累{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I'm so tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.40,0:40:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你應該閉上眼睛{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You should close your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.14,0:40:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}讓事情過去{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Let it all go.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.08,0:40:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們有時間{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We have all the time in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.06,0:41:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}彼得？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Peter?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.23,0:41:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}彼得{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Peter.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.84,0:43:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我走回來{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I walked back.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.79,0:43:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}不管接下幾小時發生什麼{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Whatever happens in the next few hours,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.36,0:43:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}不管你聽到什麼{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}whatever you hear,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.93,0:43:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們都不談論{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}we will never speak of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.40,0:44:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}議員…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.50,0:44:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}大概一個半鐘頭前  琳達告訴我{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I heard from Linda about a half an hour ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.37,0:44:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}總統要和你會面{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}The President wants to meet with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.31,0:44:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}8點30分{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}8:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.48,0:44:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}什麼事？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.88,0:44:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}不知道{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.69,0:45:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}法蘭{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.30,0:45:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}當你提出這個想法時  我並不認同{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You know, when you brought up this idea,  I wasn't sold.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.37,0:45:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}那讓我感到絕望和草率{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}It struck me as both desperate and careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.08,0:45:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}但是琳達提出所有有利的一面{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}But then Linda laid out all the pros,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.78,0:45:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他們也小心評估不利的一面{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}and they clearly outweigh the cons.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.45,0:45:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我向吉姆解釋原因  希望他不會以為我瘋了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I explained our reasoning to Jim and hoped  he wouldn't think I was off my rocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.49,0:45:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我一開始是這麼認為  不過總統提出很棒的論政{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I did at first, but the President  made some very good arguments.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.23,0:45:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}法蘭，這是很大膽的一步  很高明{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}It's a bold move, Frank. I'm very impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.33,0:45:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}長官，謝謝你這麼願意接納建言{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Well, thank you, sir,  for being open to the idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.90,0:45:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}也謝謝總統先生願意冒風險{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}And thank you, Mr. President,  for taking the risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.83,0:45:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們需要按部就班來實行{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We'll need to work this out step-by-step.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.53,0:45:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 必須完美執行  - 魯索呢？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-The execution has to be perfect.  -Where are things with Russo?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.10,0:45:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 有他的消息嗎？  - 我們仍試圖在找他{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Any word from him yet?  -We're still trying to locate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.31,0:45:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 有需要擔心的地方嗎？  - 已經兩天了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Well, is there any cause for worry?  -It's been two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.41,0:45:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我得承認我有點擔心{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I am a bit worried, I have to admit.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.08,0:45:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他這時候一定很難熬{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I mean, this must be  an extremely difficult moment for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.88,0:45:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}希望能快點找到他{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We're hoping he'll reach out shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.51,0:45:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們派人找他  我要知道他人在哪裏{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Let's get our people on it.  I want to know where he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.38,0:46:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}現在只要他一退選  我們就得趕快行動{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Now, once he withdraws,  we have to move quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.45,0:46:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們要如你提議的  發表聯合聲明{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We'll make a joint statement,  as you proposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.42,0:46:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我想這是很清楚的訊息{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}It's a clear message, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.26,0:46:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}賓州對於我們很重要  我們不能棄守{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Pennsylvanians matter to us,  and we're not gonna let them down.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.69,0:46:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}沒錯，我認為吉姆  對白宮是很重要的資產{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}That's right. I'll say that Jim's  an invaluable asset to the White House,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.76,0:46:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}但是我更欽佩他願意{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}but that I have great  admiration for the sacrifice
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.43,0:46:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}為了家鄉選民做犧牲{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}he's willing to make for  the people of his home state.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.37,0:46:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}在他當選之前  你不該接受他辭職{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}And you should not accept his  resignation until he's elected.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.10,0:46:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}這可顯示你對他的承諾不變{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}That will show  your continuing commitment to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.11,0:46:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}這是很好的想法{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I think that's a very good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.57,0:46:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}只要我能全身投入競選  我同意{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}As long as I can devote myself  wholly to the campaign, I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.11,0:46:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}要是吉姆贏了  就需要立刻提名副總統人選{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Now, should Jim win, we'll need to  nominate a Vice President immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.28,0:46:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}琳達，你有人選嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Linda, are you putting  together a list of names?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.11,0:46:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}只要你縮小人選範圍  就可以啟動調查流程{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Yes. And you can begin the vetting process  as soon as you narrow down the choices.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.65,0:46:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我已經有幾個最佳人選{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I already have a short list of top contenders.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.75,0:46:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 吉姆，我要聽聽你的意見  - 我很樂意{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-I want your input on that, Jim.  -More than happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.76,0:46:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}議員？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Congressman?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.10,0:46:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}議員？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Congressman?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.18,0:47:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們可以利用現有的基礎架構{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We can use the existing infrastructure.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.15,0:47:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你同意奈許亞倫加入嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Are you okay with Nash Aarons?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.95,0:47:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我喜歡奈許  不過我要引進一些自己的人馬{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I like Nash, but I'll want to  bring in some of my own people.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.79,0:47:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}沒問題，奈許很有團隊精神{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Well, that won't be a problem.  Nash is a team player.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.09,0:47:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們可以重新分配你現有  2016年競選連任資金…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}And we can reallocate some of your  existing 2016 reelection funds...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.43,0:47:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}抱歉，琳達{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Excuse me. Linda.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.53,0:47:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}彼得魯索死了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Peter Russo is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.40,0:47:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}自殺{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.50,0:47:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他被發現人在車庫  車子未熄火{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}He was found in his garage  with the car still running.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.91,0:47:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}法蘭，我很難過{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I'm so sorry, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.71,0:47:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 長官，我能獨處一下嗎？  - 當然{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-May I have a moment, sir?  -Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.45,0:47:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我會收集更多資料  開始起草聲明{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I will get more information  and start drafting a statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.35,0:47:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們重新安排時程  配合法蘭{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Let's reschedule. Whenever is best for Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.10,0:47:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}法蘭斯  他們發現彼得今早{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.17,0:47:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}死於自家車庫，車子未熄火{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.30,0:48:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}議員彼得魯索  今早被發現死於車庫…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Congressman Peter Russo was found dead  early this morning in the parking garage...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.74,0:48:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們怎麼沒報導這個？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Why didn't we break this?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.74,0:48:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}美國特勤局發現他的屍體{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}U.S. Secret Service Agents  discovered his body after reports that
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.68,0:48:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 魯索從週六就失蹤  - 可惡！{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Russo had been missing since Saturday.  -Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.68,0:48:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他的屍體被移往  華府驗屍官辦公室{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}His body was transferred  to the D. C. Coroner's office
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.42,0:48:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}進行驗屍  確認他是死因是自殺{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}where an autopsy is expected  to confirm his death as a suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.29,0:48:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}出身費城的新進議員…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}A junior congressman from Philadelphia...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.19,0:48:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 享年36歲  - 喬伊，看這個{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Russo was 36 years old...  -Zoe. Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.60,0:48:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}…育有兩名子女{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}...and is survived by two children.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.00,0:48:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 我得到辦公室  - 魯索之前投入賓州州長{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-I gotta get to the office.  -Russo was in the midst of a heated battle
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.67,0:48:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}競爭激烈的選戰中{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}for the governorship of Pennsylvania.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.04,0:48:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}最後一次公開談話  是在匹茲堡WZPZ電台{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}He was last heard publicly during  a morning political radio show
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.37,0:48:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}晨間政論廣播節目{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}on Pittsburgh station WZPZ.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.08,0:48:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}在專訪中，他口齒不清  態度恍神…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Now, during the interview, he slurred  his words, he sounded disoriented...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.28,0:48:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 克裏絲汀娜  - …讓許多人相信{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Christina.  -...Ieading many to believe
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.38,0:48:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 他被換掉…  - 請幫我買回華府的火車票{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-that he had relapsed...  -Can you get me a train back to D.C.?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.62,0:48:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}本電視台為你播報關於  議員彼得魯索自殺{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Right here on this TV station  for all your late-breaking details
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.02,0:48:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}這則重大新聞  所有最新的及時消息{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}about this major news story,  the suicide of Congressman Peter Russo.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.10,0:49:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}接電話  回答我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.20,0:49:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他們發現彼得今早在車庫  車子未熄火{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.61,0:49:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}回家中{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.13,0:51:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我現在難以表達感受{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I find it very difficult to express  everything that I'm feeling right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.40,0:51:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我知道克萊兒有同樣的感覺{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}and I know Claire feels exactly the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.41,0:51:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}彼得對我們來說非常特別{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Peter was very special to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.21,0:51:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}只要跟他接觸  所有人都會被他吸引{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}A sort of magnetic presence  that electrified everyone he touched.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.91,0:51:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我老公和我在過去幾個月裏  和他感情很好{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}And my husband and I became very  close to him in the past several months.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.52,0:51:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}彼得不只是同事、朋友{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Peter was more than a colleague,  more than a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.62,0:51:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他是家人{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}He was family.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.86,0:51:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們的心  和他的子女、母親同在{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Our hearts go out to his children  and to his mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.63,0:51:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}也和認識他的人  和他共事的人、愛他的人同在{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}to all of those who knew him  and worked with him and loved him.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.66,0:51:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}希望大家尊重  他們的隱私和損失{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We would ask that all of you respect  their privacy and honor their loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.70,0:51:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}今天對於美國國會、對於賓州{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Today is indeed a sad day  for the United States Congress,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.17,0:51:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}還有我們所有人來說  是悲傷的一天{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}for the state of Pennsylvania,  and for all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.14,0:51:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}感謝大家{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Thank you very much.

